breadCrumbs.text: Upload or link any additional documentation

errortext:
There is a problem with these files
Your file cannot exceed 300MB
You have exceeded the maximum upload of 1GB for your files
title: Upload documents (Optional)
subtitle: You can upload documents or add links to other web pages that will help a supplier to better understand your procurement
filedesc: you can upload as many files as you need to, up to a maximum of 1Gb in total. You can only use the following file formats: csv, doc, docx, jpg, jpeg, kml, ods, odt, pdf, png, ppt, pptx, rdf, rtf, txt, xls, xlsx, xml, zip
